Text:
Gwen Summers is the star of this show by playing a very young, inexperienced girl ("I've never done this kind of thing before" giggle giggle). If you can get past that theme (often repeated), the last part of the video proves she has done it many times (and done very well). Jade Marcella is slutty while Ann Marie plays the cute girl-next-door.
Video quality is very good; sound is up and down particularly on Ann Marie.
Definite D/L for HJ collection.
